  • Konstruktordetails

    • Caregiver

      public Caregiver(String firstName, String surname, String phoneNumber)
      Constructor to initiate an object of class Caregiver with the given parameter. Use this constructor to initiate objects, which are not persisted yet, because it will not have a caregiver id (caregiverID).
      Parameter:
      firstName - First name of the caregiver.
      surname - Last name of the caregiver.
      phoneNumber - phone number of the caregiver.

    • Caregiver

      public Caregiver(long caregiverID, String firstName, String surname, String phoneNumber)
      Constructor to initiate an object of class Patient with the given parameter. Use this constructor to initiate objects, which are already persisted and have a caregiver id (caregiverID).
      Parameter:
      caregiverID - Caregiver id.
      firstName - First name of the caregiver.
      surname - Last name of the caregiver.
      phoneNumber - phone number of the caregiver.
